<br>
Spells Memmed:<br>
<br>
51 Earth<br>
49 Earth<br>
49 Air<br>
Sheild of Lava<br>
Lava Bolt<br>
Burnout 3<br>
Gate<br>
Malosi<br>
<br>
<br>
Cast your biggest, best 51 earth pet, try him out on furies beforehand, get a 58 hitter ) give him a burnout 3, med to full, summon yourself a mod rod, med again to full, lava shield pet, med to full, pull him with malosi, send pet, sit down.<br>
<br>
Then, when pet is about 30 % health, cast another 51 earth, lava shield quick and run to other side of the island, have pet targeted.  When pet dies, cast a new pet, this time a 49 earth pet, burnout 3 on it, and lava shield.  Wait for Alli, send in pet, eat mod rod, run to other side of island.<br>
<br>
Cast 49 air, burnout 3 /pet no taunt, when alli comes back, he'll be chasing YOU for a long time because when your pet dies, agro passes to YOU, so all that damage done is as if it was done from the mage personally, so think of it as doing a big ass 5K nuke against him and then sending pet in.  Pet aint gonna taunt for CRAP ! for ages, lol, so he'll get in lots of free hits, just make sure you dont run too far away from the alli, otherwise sheer range will make him turn to pet instead, and this will mess up the whole process. Usually when i did this, it took me 2 x 51 earth pets, 1 - 2 x 49 earth pets, and usually 2 49 air pets at the end.  If you're feeling really special, you can kill your pet too so you get the full xp, but this is in no way an exp camp, this is for if you need some gems and stuff, just cash, etc, or if the price of blue diamonds has gone up too much and you need some resist gear.<br>
<br>
BTW, I went here later on when i got epic at 56, epic pet once it's damage shielded and has burnout 4 on soloed the damn thing ) he did it 3 times in a row, so if it was blind luck, well, lets just say it probably wasn't... not worth the time investment, only for bragging rights to be cool =)<br>
<br>
